{"tid":1245277,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無不反對通知書","createTime":"2019-06-20T08:46:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T08:51:43.000Z","uid":114186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bbca0b399679793b04616aae11a703185cb2836b","tid":1245277,"uid":114186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T08:46:33.000Z","msg":"會唔會比人話非法集結強行清場?"},{"pid":"8870646927a1add65f2c2cf9e4099d08066b86ff","tid":1245277,"uid":114186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T08:47:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e265bd6e81e31a874e417dd1558a3e59af17def3","tid":1245277,"uid":114186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T08:50:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ef35ad309fa83c861c7d034dfba3b44ee4ad807","tid":1245277,"uid":18948,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T08:51:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.doj.gov.hk/chi/archive/doc/201200c.doc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.doj.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Farchive%2Fdoc%2F201200c.doc&d=cvYurzZEI7gK%2Fp8SijS8D5mLjsYRFZgpJr%2B2v3iO%2BBA%3D&h=00d78456\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.doj.gov.hk/chi/archive/doc/201200c.doc</a><br />\n<br />\n3.​最普遍的誤解，是公眾遊行必須得到警方批准。我希望所有議員現在明白，事實並非如此。《公安條例》只是就大部分超過30人的公眾遊行，訂立了一項通知警方的規定。<br />\n<br />\n4.​警務處處長在接到舉行公眾遊行的意向通知後，除非反對舉行遊行，否則必須發出不反對通知書。如果處長在指定期限內沒有發出不反對通知書，也沒有發出反對遊行的通知，他便會被當作已發出不反對通知書。<br />\n<br />\n5.​換言之，如果警方不發出反對通知，遊行便可進行，顯而易見，法例並無規定遊行必須得到警方批准。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">究竟要講幾多次</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"4226f3e2532950d0fc2a0fc4400b913cf3bd4e34","tid":1245277,"uid":52477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T08:51:15.000Z","msg":"@燕夕"},{"pid":"e18e5ca2138509c3901ce53d0fb29e320c247ca3","tid":1245277,"uid":57274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T08:51:43.000Z","msg":"[終極懶人包] 621須知！抗爭及法律手冊回帶<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1245129\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1245129</a>"}]}